high_descs: Turn left and head towards the television against the far wall.
Pick up the pen that is inside the stand upon which the television rests.
Turn around and head towards the near right corner of the dining table behind the sofa.
Place the pan on the plate that is placed on the near right corner of the dining table.
Pick up the plate with the pen.
Turn around and head towards the three-shelf glass table in front of the sofa.
Place the pen and plate on the middle shelf of the glass table.
anns.task_desc: Gather a pen and plate and put them on a table.

high_descs: Turn right, then walk towards the chair, then left, then walk towards the television.
Pick up the pen from underneath the television stand in front of the Kleenex.
Turn all the way around, walk towards the door, then head towards the glass table.
Place the pen onto the plate near the edge of the table.
Pick the plate up with the pen on it.
Turn around then walk towards the green chair, turn right, then face the glass table.
Place the plate with the pen on it underneath the glass coffee table
anns.task_desc: Place a plate and a pen underneath a glass coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk towards the chair, then hang a left and walk up to the glass table the television on.
Pick up the black pen off of the bottom shelf of the glass table.
Walk forward, then turn left and walk around the couch to the large glass dining table.
Put the black pen on the white plate that is closest to you on the glass dining table.
Pick up the white plate with the pen on it.
Turn left and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk over to the coffee table.
Put the white plate with the pen on it on the middle shelf of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a white plate with a pen on it on a shelf of the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and make your way to the front of the tv and then face it.
Pick up the pen from the left side of the tv stand.
Turn left and move to the back of the couch and then face the table.
Place the pen on the plate near the edge of the table closest to you.
Pick up the plate.
Turn right and make your way to the coffee table in front of the couch facing the yellow vase.
Place the plate on the left side of the middle shelf of the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pen on a plate and put it on the coffee table's middle shelf.

high_descs: Turn left, walk towards the tv stand, stand in front of the tv.
Pick up the pen in front of the tissue box in the tv stand.
Turn around, walk past the sofa towards the dining table.
Place the pen on the plate that is not next to the bowl.
Pick up the plate with the pen on it.
Turn around, walk past the sofa, turn right towards the coffee table.
Place the plate in the middle shelf of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put the pen on a plate  into the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward toward the chair, then to the television on the left
pick up the pen on the left side of the bottom shelf
turn left and walk toward the chair, then turn left, go past the couch to the dining table
place the pen on the plate that's not next to the bowl
pick up the plate with pen on it
turn to the right, walk past the couch
place the plate with the pen on the middle shelf directly under the black bowl
anns.task_desc: Place a pen on a plate, place them on the middle shelf of coffee table
